《'''两女一杯'''》（{{Lang-en|''2 Girls 1 Cup''}}），2007年[[巴西|巴西]]色情片《饥饿婊子》（{{Lang-en|''Hungry Bitches''}}）的[[预告片|预告片]]，由MFX媒体（MFX Media）發行。预告片中包含兩[[嗜糞癖|嗜糞癖]]女子相互爱抚，吞吃对方的[[糞便|排遺物]]，然后呕吐到对方嘴里的情节<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=2 Girls, 1 Cup: The Real Poop|url=http://www.thesmokinggun.com/documents/revolting/2-girls-1-cup-real-poop|accessdate=2019-03-14|author=|date=2010-10-07|work=The Smoking Gun|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190116144005/http://www.thesmokinggun.com/documents/revolting/2-girls-1-cup-real-poop|archivedate=2019-01-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

該片通过網路在各大[[網誌|網誌]]和[[留言板|留言板]]上病毒式传播，不少网友将自己或他人观看视频的反应录制下来，并上传到各个视频分享网站，引起巨大反響，成為網路[[迷因|迷因]]<ref name="McGill">{{cite news|first=Kathryn|last=Amey|title=POP RHETORIC: Cute with Chris vs 2 girls, 1 cup|publisher=The McGill Tribune|url=http://media.www.mcgilltribune.com/media/storage/paper234/news/2007/12/04/AE/Pop-Rhetoric.Cute.With.Chris.Vs.2.Girls.1.Cup-3129312.shtml|date=2007-12-04|accessdate=2007-12-07|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5mqnnIcZd?url=http://media.www.mcgilltribune.com/media/storage/paper234/news/2007/12/04/AE/Pop-Rhetoric.Cute.With.Chris.Vs.2.Girls.1.Cup-3129312.shtml|archivedate=2010-01-17|deadurl=yes}}</ref>。2007年10月[[旬|中旬]]左右，[[YouTube|YouTube]]上的反應和聲討達到頂峰<ref>{{Cite web|title=Karina’s Capsule: 2 Girls 1 Cup Reactions|url=https://gigaom.com/2007/11/20/karinas-capsule-2-girls-1-cup-reactions/|accessdate=2019-03-14|author=|date=2007-11-20|last=Longworth|first=Karina|work=gigaom.com|language=en-US|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712155150/https://gigaom.com/2007/11/20/karinas-capsule-2-girls-1-cup-reactions/|archivedate=2018-07-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
视频导演马可·维拉诺瓦（Marco Villanova）原名马尔科·安东尼奥·菲奥里托（Marco Antônio Fiorito），1971年7月1日生于巴西[[聖保羅_(巴西)|聖保羅]]，自称有“强迫性[[戀物|戀物癖]]”。1994年，菲奥里托对电影制作产生兴趣，两年后和妻子霍埃尔玛·布里托（Joelma Brito，艺名莱蒂西娅·hwjassss制片商MFX视频（MFX Video）便是其中之一<ref name=":0" />。

==影响==
经常有观众认为，片中的“粪便”实际上是食物做的，比如炸豆泥、[[冰淇淋|冰淇淋]]、[[花生酱|花生酱]]等等<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.co.za/books?id=ADv_AwAAQBAJ&pg=PA68|publisher=Oxford University Press|date=2015|isbn=9780199914760|language=en|first=Adrienne|last=Evans|first2=Sarah|last2=Riley|title=Technologies of Sexiness: Sex, Identity, and Consumer Culture|accessdate=2019-03-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712121921/https://books.google.co.za/books?id=ADv_AwAAQBAJ&pg=PA68|archivedate=2018-07-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。马可·维拉诺瓦后来在法庭上辩称，“粪便”实际上是巧克力冰淇淋，未获法院采纳<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.co.za/books?id=GZXSBQAAQBAJ&pg=PA49|publisher=CRC Press|date=2014-12-03|isbn=9781482260021|language=en|first=Carmen M.|last=Cusack|title=Pornography and The Criminal Justice System|accessdate=2019-03-18|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712124813/https://books.google.co.za/books?id=GZXSBQAAQBAJ&pg=PA49|archivedate=2018-07-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。现在看来，这段视频中呈现的很有可能就是真实的[[嗜糞癖|嗜糞癖]]<ref>{{Cite web|title=‘2 Girls, 1 Cup’: An Investigation Into the Web’s Shittiest Mystery|url=https://melmagazine.com/en-us/story/2-girls-1-cup-an-investigation-into-the-webs-shittiest-mystery|work=MEL Magazine|date=2017-05-15|accessdate=2019-03-14|language=en-US|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190211103410/https://melmagazine.com/en-us/story/2-girls-1-cup-an-investigation-into-the-webs-shittiest-mystery|archivedate=2019-02-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

这部视频后来有很多模仿和恶搞，最著名的一个便是《四女手指画》，视频中有四个女人，情节与《两女一杯》相似。此外，《两女一杯》还为类似视频的命名提供了灵感，比如《两男一马》《两女一指》《三男一锤》《八女无杯》等等<ref name="pornencyc">{{cite book|last=Duthel|first=Heinz|date=2010-11-12|title=The Complete Internet Pornography Encyclopedia|url=http://www.fishpond.com.au/Books/Complete-Internet-Pornography-Encyclopedia-Heinz-Duthel/9780557672370|publisher=ePublications|isbn=978-0-557-65507-6|accessdate=2014-12-04|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20141223165420/http://www.fishpond.com.au/Books/Complete-Internet-Pornography-Encyclopedia-Heinz-Duthel/9780557672370|archivedate=2014-12-23}}</ref>。吉他手[[約翰·梅爾|約翰·梅爾]]在博客上传了一个题为《两男一杯》的视频，和喜剧演员{{tsl|en|Sherrod Small|謝羅德·斯摩爾}}模仿原视频中的两名女子吃[[粉紅莓冰品店|粉紅莓]][[霜凍優格|冻酸奶]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.chartattack.com/news/44822/john-mayer-enters-food-porn-world-with-2-guys-1-cup|work=www.chartattack.com|accessdate=2019-03-15|title=John Mayer Enters Food Porn World With "2 Guys 1 Cup"|archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5mqnnTCG8?url=http://www.chartattack.com/news/44822/john-mayer-enters-food-porn-world-with-2-guys-1-cup|archivedate=2010-01-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="mayer">{{cite web|url=http://www.johnmayer.com/blog#1560|title=Team JM Blog " John Mayer – Battle Studies|publisher=Johnmayer.com|date=2007-07-14|accessdate=2011-07-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110711102201/http://www.johnmayer.com/blog#1560|archivedate=2011-07-11|deadurl=yes}}</ref>；美国喜剧人[[柯南·奥布莱恩|柯南·奥布莱恩]]为他的网站Conan.XXX拍了部《一男两碗》，片中主演[[安迪·里希特|安迪·里希特]]喝了两碗汤<ref>{{Citation|title=One Guy, Two Bowls: CONAN.XXX|url=http://teamcoco.com/node/37181|accessdate=2019-03-15|language=en}}</ref>。加拿大喜剧人{{tsl|en|Jon Lajoie|乔恩·拉乔伊}}作了首《两女一杯之歌》，歌颂原视频中两女子“伟大的爱情”，[[YouTube|YouTube]]播放量已逾千万<ref>{{Citation|title=2 Girls 1 Cup Song|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wxp3zqIqO68&t=0h0m0s|date=2007-11-01|accessdate=2019-03-15|last=JonLajoie|archive-date=2019-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190318123406/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=wxp3zqIqO68&t=0h0m0s}}</ref>。

达尼洛·克罗塞（Danilo Croce）是菲奥里托在美公司高管，因销售、播送、运输淫秽物品，于2006年和2007年被[[美國聯邦政府|美國聯邦政府]]提起三次诉讼，最终判处三年无监督缓刑，没收公司资产9萬8000美元<ref>{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.co.za/books?id=GZXSBQAAQBAJ&pg=PA49#v=onepage&q&f=false|publisher=CRC Press|date=2014-12-03|isbn=9781482260021|language=en|first=Carmen M.|last=Cusack|title=Pornography and The Criminal Justice System|accessdate=2019-03-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180712124813/https://books.google.co.za/books?id=GZXSBQAAQBAJ&pg=PA49#v=onepage&q&f=false|archivedate=2018-07-12|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

